    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, but it's a bit too generic. For the part about why meritocracy doesn't work to solve this, can you write a paragraph that basically explains why the idea of a \"meritocracy\" is actually just a myth used to justify current inequalities? I want it to sound really impactful, like it's exposing a fundamental truth.",
